Installation
---------------------------------------------------------------------
To install bitext-compression you need to have installed the
following packages:

....

Once you have all the required software installed, install
bitext-compression in the common way:

$ ./configure && make

and as a root

# make install

For more information on each program execute it without parameters.

 Good luck!

